snippet.title: Brutal Doom: Hell On Earth Starter Pack - Doom Mod Madness
snippet.description:
Oh sure you've probably played Brutal Doom in some form or another by now but have you experienced the glory of a fully featured 32 level custom campaign? This is one Doom Mod that takes you on a hell of a journey.

HELL ON EARTH STARTER PACK
